{"tid":1010465,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚有梅西！巴塞國王盃著中文版波衫","createTime":"2019-02-06T04:17:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T08:19:16.000Z","uid":3454,"like":4,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cd77c8f48ebbb54d1b0244b54cf6b8515022d584","tid":1010465,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:17:10.000Z","msg":"今晚有梅西！巴塞國王盃著中文版波衫<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5E6pPth.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5E6pPth.jpg&h=c80ad231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTKZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=db70cf16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】巴塞隆拿在周三西班牙國王盃4強首回合迎擊對皇家馬德里時，球衣上的名字將印上中文字。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙盃4強首回合的國家打吡「上集」，由巴塞隆拿主場迎戰皇家馬德里，由於剛好是中國新年的緣故，巴塞方面決定穿上特別版的戰衣落場，該球衣除了英文名和號碼等外，還特別印上中文名字，印在英文名和球衣號碼之間。<br />\n<br />\n當然，球員的中文名用的是國內譯名，球會官方Twitter還上載印製球衣的過程，其中看到美斯（Lionel Messi）的10號球衣，中文名是「梅西」，此外還有皮克（碧基）等等。Twitter編輯還以簡體字寫道：為慶祝中國新年，明晚的國家打吡紅藍軍團將身披印有中文名字的球衣。<br />\n<br />\n中國和亞洲是歐洲勁旅爭相滲透的市場，巴塞今夏就將訪問中國和日本，進行季前備戰。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : Twitter圖片<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=24490082095\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D24490082095&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTKZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=f255af3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=24490082095</a><br />\n<br />\n屌奶星 枉我地CC台手足撐加泰獨立<br />\n死疤狗而家走去奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c3d27138b810eaaf6741c5a394cc7649edd875","tid":1010465,"uid":200801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:21:03.000Z","msg":"好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2753eb8b77f06014ebed4deaed1ff11c1deb6503","tid":1010465,"uid":35176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T